{"tid":472758,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★支那開始規範 婆乸舞！","createTime":"2017-11-18T13:58:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-18T16:06:34.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fa62fd186e9cce2c6217d7e54d7e3b0ecfb5a0e2","tid":472758,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T13:58:25.000Z","msg":"公共場合播歌跳舞亦可能造成擾民，甚至曾經引發打鬥 。國家體育總局近日發出通知，進一步規範廣場舞活動，列明有哪一些地方不准跳廣場舞，亦禁止跳舞時產生噪音。<br />\n<br />\n位於廣州越秀區的起義烈士陵園，墓園區內及門外都禁止任何娛樂活動。至於墓園北面的休閒區，陵園按照《廣州公園條例》設立不同的功能分區，其中在聲功能區允許群眾跳舞、唱歌，但設有時段及音量限制，不過仍有市民覺得不太合適。<br />\n<br />\n有廣州市民表示︰「這裡是英雄墓地，比較莊嚴點、肅靜點。」另一廣州市民指︰「稍為應該要控制一下是真的，有時候覺得真的覺得太嘈。」<br />\n<br />\n國家體育總局近日發出通知，指為推動廣場舞活動健康發展，將作出進一步規範，包括禁止在烈士陵園等莊嚴場所跳廣場舞，跳舞所產生的噪音亦不可影響周邊學生上課和居民正常生活。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/greaterchina/5a10210de603830220659585/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fgreaterchina%2F5a10210de603830220659585%2F&d=r%2BjOIL3uSG4XGXMNl6bmEjM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=b06a9bf0\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/greaterchina/5a10210de603830220659585/</a>"},{"pid":"63f63b7b661db765cac47a647974366d4e13090f","tid":472758,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T13:58:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62719510e823a1c4d20e7153b158bd2126e68f10","tid":472758,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T14:03:27.000Z","msg":"冇人理樓豬，捱義氣推吓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f945db867c826cd8b0dfe1e615ed7f5ead96742f","tid":472758,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T14:04:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇人理樓豬，捱義氣推吓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br 